    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部落生存竞技场 + 建牌器，能行吗？我认为可以，这款游戏也证明了这一点。自定义你的卡牌库，在成群的外星人中生存下来，他们甚至比你还陌生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一种可能的组合可能是这样的  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/da1674aaab50f242495fdb8f666e502d.poster.avif?t=1743970812\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/da1674aaab50f242495fdb8f666e502d.webm?t=1743970812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/da1674aaab50f242495fdb8f666e502d.mp4?t=1743970812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进步</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新卡牌，自定义你的跑动牌组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新个性，彻底改变下一次运行时的最佳构建方式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁更高难度，更多外星人、更多回合、更多乐趣和更多随机性（更大的牌库）</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在运行中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受 15-120 秒的短促动作浪潮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级，从随机选择的 3 种升级中选择基本角色属性的提升方向</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在回合之间从商店购买卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开始为生存而战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为不可阻挡的力量，否则就只有死路一条</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圆形</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过摧毁尽可能多的外星人来赚取 XP 和一种奇怪的货币形式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要么努力生存，要么疯狂杀戮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可激活的卡牌进行以下任一操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久增强角色力量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >临时获得大威力加成和组合技</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或释放毁灭性的特殊攻击</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/3cd807cbc7d7bf900b423fbefe8b57e6.poster.avif?t=1743970812\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/3cd807cbc7d7bf900b423fbefe8b57e6.webm?t=1743970812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232320/extras/3cd807cbc7d7bf900b423fbefe8b57e6.mp4?t=1743970812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运行之间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新难度、角色和卡片</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义下次运行时商店可容纳的牌库</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查看您之前的运行情况，并与您的好友比较您的成绩</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proudly Powered by Godot Game Engine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made in Germany</p>",
